  <!-- 核心特性 -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">为什么不是另一个聊天壳</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">六层工程能力，把"和模型对话"变成"指挥一个工程团队"</p>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
        <h3>专家团，不是独白</h3>
        <p>Leader 理解目标、拆任务、建 DAG、调度专家；Worker 各司其职——架构、后端、前端、研究、QA、审查。13 种预设角色，每个 Worker 有独立上下文和工具链。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="12" r="3"/><line x1="6" y1="9" x2="6" y2="15"/><line x1="9" y1="6" x2="15" y2="11"/><line x1="9" y1="18" x2="15" y2="13"/></svg></div>
        <h3>DAG 让复杂可调度</h3>
        <p>目标自动拆解为带依赖的任务图。无依赖的并行跑，有依赖的按序解锁。每个任务有 owner、状态、阻塞关系、结果回执——不是一串线性对话。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/></svg></div>
        <h3>三端同一份状态</h3>
        <p>WebUI、TUI、CLI 不各自猜状态。SSE + ACP JSON-RPC 把 session、leader、worker、task、permission 统一到一个运行态快照，流式事件负责体验，快照负责校准。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>真实工具，不是嘴上说说</h3>
        <p>100+ 内置工具在权限系统下运行：文件读写、Shell、Git、浏览器自动化、Office/PDF、Workflow 画布、MCP 统一入口。Agent 的每一步都有日志和证据。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg></div>
        <h3>验收闭环，不是"说完成就完成"</h3>
        <p>每个任务完成时触发结构化验收：PASS/FAIL/BLOCKED。投机执行跑多分支择优，对抗验证做退出码断言，契约五阶段闭环——contract → implement → evaluate → repair → reset。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div>
        <h3>MCP Forge + Skills</h3>
        <p>模板驱动生成 MCP Server：需求 → 模板 → 生成 → 沙箱 → Inspector → 注册。Skills 四层优先级自动注入 Worker 上下文。不是插件市场摆设，是运行时能力。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

